  "texts": [
    "In addition, universities in regions with limited access to ChatGPT may have more concerns, particularly when they take the initiative to provide staff and students with access to use ChatGPT.",
    "Using the situation in Hong Kong as an example, universities have varying approaches to offering different versions of ChatGPT to their staff and students.",
    "This raises questions such as how many tokens should be granted to ensure sufficiency, how long will this service be available, and how many other GenAI tools should be provided in the future.",
    "ImplicationsThis study aims to make recommendations to universities in making policies and management based on the findings.",
    "Three practical implications are listed below."
  ]
}